{
  "stem": "9.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I grab few cans of paint and put it in front of me, and laid down completely still.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They looked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They looked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was-- my heart was beating so loud that I was afraid that's what they're going hear.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because I wasn't breathing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Somehow, the death did not have me on the list.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because this was the first encounter with death at that point.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they did not discover me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Many other incidents happened later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But anyway, right now, what I want to tell you is myself being a young girl, the Germans wanted to use my strengths-- my muscles.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they selected me to break large boulders into tiny little rocks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They would give me a big hammer-- a mallet, you call it-- or a pick.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I had all of these tools.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And all day long I would pound these huge, big rocks with my two hands.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I developed tremendous muscles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I was so strong that I was ashamed of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And as a result of that, as I started going to different experiences through the war, I was able to do various things, because I was strong.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And maybe part of it saved me, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Because as you will hear later, I was continuously sent to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These were people who thought that they're going to save their own life by being Jewish policemen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So all the Germans had to do was come over and give orders.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would like to have today 500 Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You organize them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these men went out into the public and brought 500 people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When the Germans were coming at night, or when these policemen were bringing the people, all people were told is that they're going to work-- no address, no location.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
